1. Create rss directory under your WHMCS root
2. Copy the files rss.php and class.rss.php to this directory
3. Open a browser to your WHMCS site with /rss/rss.php appended:

   http://IP ADDRESS/whmcs/rss/rss.php?Username=admin&Password=admin&Dept=2

   Username = An administrator
   Password = Password :)
   Dept = Department Number. If you specify Dept=0 then it will pass all authorised departments



